            "notes": "This deck revolves around using Animar, Soul of Elements as the commander to generate infinite mana with creatures that reduce the cost of other creatures, such as Bloom Tender and Bloodstained Mire. By continually casting and bouncing Ancestral Statue with Animar's ability, you can draw your entire deck and find a win condition like Walking Ballista or Purphoros, God of the Forge to close out the game. The deck is packed with mana dorks, tutors, and combo pieces to quickly assemble the infinite mana combo and secure a victory. The strategy focuses on ramping quickly, protecting your combo pieces, and disrupting your opponent's game plan to achieve a dominant position in the game."
